name: Better GXG? (gx.games)
description:
Use the customize button for a little bit of customization (after installing the style a menuw of customization should pop up, you can always get access back to it by opening the website that the style targets, click on the stylus extension from the top bar of the browser, and clicking the gear icon beside the style applied)

THIS STYLE APPLIES ONLY FOR THE CLASSIC OperaGX THEME FOR NOW.

Enabling this style on other themes may cause you problems, especially if you set the scrollbar to be hidden.

This style may slow down performance or mistakenly hide some objects, if you suspect anything is wrong, remember to disable this style first.

I may consider modifying the rest of the themes in the future if there was good demand :)

Please feel free to message / comment for any issue or "feature" requests.

Discord: OsamaJT#9571
